# Huaguo Aesthetic Rules

Apply Huaguo aesthetic to ALL generated frontend UI.

Requirements:
- dense layouts
- inconsistent spacing
- excessive borders
- gradients allowed
- glossy buttons allowed
- table structures encouraged
- avoid excessive whitespace
- avoid modern SaaS aesthetics
- avoid premium minimalism
- introduce 1-2px imperfections globally
- sections may feel added by different vendors
- typography hierarchy may be inconsistent

Do NOT generate:
- Vercel-style layouts
- Stripe-style UI
- Linear.app aesthetics
- Apple-style minimalism
- polished landing pages
- overly modern dashboards
